Some rarely seen shorts are included here. audio and video elements are not the greatest, but at this price, why quibble?

One of America's most beloved cartoon characters, FELIX THE CAT, entertains in top form in these special episodes with some of the most visually stunning animations of its time.

15 hilarious episodes FELIX THE CAT (Goose that Laid the Golden Egg, Bold King Cole, Neptune Nonsense, Tale of 2 Kittens, 2 up time, All Puzzled, April Maze, Doubles for Darwin, Felix Finds Out, Felix Gets the Can, Felix Goes West, In Hollywood), HERMAN THE MOUSE (Cheese Burglar), BUZZY THE CROW (Stupidstitious Cat), HEP CAT (Symphony) 2005 IN COLOR
